What is Termux? Termux is a Terminal Emulator which can be used on Android.
Why Termux?  &ldquo;Start by answering the Whys&rdquo;- Simon Sinek
 Termux is quite useful if you are a aspiring dev and doesn&rsquo;t have a budget to buy a laptop or If your machine goes on frequent strikes(as for me). You can do mostly anything that you do in a Linux terminal, like exploring files,editing them,moving them and using tools for Python,C,JavaScript(Node) etc&hellip;
